
A goat cannot eat coconut because it cannot climb up a ladder to reach the coconuts up in the coconut tree.
(Swahili: Mbuzi hali nazi kwa vile hawezi kupanda ngazi ndipo azifikie nazi.)

The black goat steps on the rock. The big rock breaks into four (pieces). This is how the goat's head should break. Like the the rock breaks into four.
(Romanian: Capra neagră calcă-n piatră,Piatra mare crapă-n patru.Aşa să crape capul caprei,Cum a crăpat piatra-n patru.)

The stone breaks the goat, the goat breaks the stone.
(Romanian: Piatra crapă capra, capra crapă piatra.)
